title: The Natural Cafe - San Luis Obispo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Several locations in California. Extensive menu includes many vegetarian dishes: sandwiches, salads, pasta, pizza, veg tacos, veggie sandwiches, smoothies, a veggie soup of the day (sometimes vegan). You can ask to veganize a dish using veganaise, etc. Order at the counter, and food is brought to your table. Very spacious interior with high ceiling, natural oak furniture, and oil painting on walls.
